               <p>The prisoner has been <rs id="t17871212-67-deflabel322" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871212-67-defend573 t17871212-67-deflabel322"></join> to me these three years: he came and told me he wished to leave me, he did not care to stay in my works and longer: I told him he must not go yet; one of my clerks informed me he had secreted a slab of copper, and I detected him. I asked him where he intended to sell it, he said in Long-lane.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17871212-67-person579">
