                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>All I know is by his own confession.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Mr. Cox promised me that I should have favour.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. I said, if you will disclose your confederates, you may receive more favour with the Court me! says he; that was all he said.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17871212-67-person580">
